column2: SELECT   COUNT(*) FROM galSpecInfo AS i  JOIN galSpecLine AS l ON l.specObjID = i.specObjID WHERE   i.dec BETWEEN #. AND +#  AND i.reliable > #  AND l.nii_#_flux > #*l.nii_#_flux_err  AND oiii_flux > #*oiii_flux_err  AND h_beta_flux > #*h_beta_flux_err  AND oiii_flux > #  AND h_beta_flux > #  AND LOG1#(oiii_flux/NULLIF(h_beta_flux,#)) > #
